{"tid":1408955,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女權團體：平機會不作為，要不要一起去圍警署？","createTime":"2019-08-04T18:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T19:03:24.000Z","uid":72730,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"394da23d7d582ea3be31a9952e2f9d986fd02933","tid":1408955,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:52:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分享自性/別公義委員會Facebook</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n性/別公義委員會Gender and Sexual Justice in Action<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gendersexjustice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgendersexjustice%2F&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHad3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=4c65e97b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gendersexjustice/</a><br />\n<br />\n6月底，性公會曾與多個關注性別議題的本地團體聯署譴責警察以性暴力鎮壓示威者。7月中，我們到平機會請願，遞交聯署，並在平機會自製連儂牆表達訴求，促請當局徹查及處理警察濫用性暴力的問題。 <br />\n<br />\n數日前，我們終於收到朱敏健主席的回信：「平機會並沒有足夠資料對指稱事件作出跟進。」這就是我們的平機會，抗爭者受到性騷擾，我們去投訴，就是會得到這種答案。 <br />\n<br />\n今天晚上，香港人再一次在網上直播中一同看到被捕女子被防暴警察扯脫褲子，公然侮辱。在平機會不作為的情況下，我們可以做甚麼？大家要不要一起去圍警署？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RvrStvy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvrStvy.png&h=127ea1e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJ1GmQz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJ1GmQz.png&h=4abe4f08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5dddf1b0d8d5903843e5d9c5acf9bbb92c48cf9","tid":1408955,"uid":108337,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:53:47.000Z","msg":"在平機會不作為的情況下，我們可以做甚麼？大家要不要一起去圍警署？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要</span>"},{"pid":"086611583388e4faa6f830d8452e48696ec3ee4d","tid":1408955,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:54:51.000Z","msg":"圍埋平機會"},{"pid":"056b0f7c05f1a4293fb7d83b7eed5cdb0fc903d3","tid":1408955,"uid":13750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"女士們 買定隻哨子/電哨旁身呀！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1408534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1408534</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好撚心痛呀 保護自己呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b72e9c945eea8edc28d218efcb4d73a13909eb7","tid":1408955,"uid":157938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"全民dm Emma Watson. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/emmawatson?igshid=b5y3xa4gke0u\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Femmawatson%3Figshid%3Db5y3xa4gke0u&d=uztthH5CN7iuCFQPSeIHad3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=72dabe1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/emmawatson?igshid=b5y3xa4gke0u</a><br />\n<br />\nIG傳送門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHello Emma,<br />\n<br />\nWe're writing to express concern over an incident involving the violation of female rights that has just happened in Hong Kong. As you may have noticed, Hong Kongers are currently experiencing police brutality on a daily basis during the process of fighting aginst the extradition bill imposed by the HK government. Earlier just now a female protestor was arrested near a local police station, during which her pants were violently ripped off against her will. The police officers made no attempt to protect her privacy which was unacceptable on any level. Since the beginning of the protests in June not one of our local feminist organizations have stood out for female rights. <br />\n<br />\nWe are in desperate times and sincerely seek your help in raising international concern over this matter as we can foresee more inicidents like this one are going to happen in the near future if nothing is done to stop police brutality. Thanks a lot for your time!<br />\n<br />\nA group of concerned Hong Kongers"},{"pid":"b554a20f18c0c4e23a093ba8af9b33b71ee6c87d","tid":1408955,"